Authorisation
The following products are authorised for the purposes of Article 4(2) and Article 16(2) of Regulation (EC) No 1829/2003 in accordance with the conditions set out in this Decision:
(a) foods and food ingredients containing, consisting of, or produced from DAS-Ø15Ø7-1xDAS-59122-7 maize;
(b) feed containing, consisting of, or produced from DAS-Ø15Ø7-1xDAS-59122-7 maize;
(c) products other than food and feed containing or consisting of DAS-Ø15Ø7-1xDAS-59122-7 maize for the same uses as any other maize with the exception of cultivation.
